ight:bold;&quot;&gt;　　4、他不让你承担他的痛苦&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　这个男人不但能够照顾你，而且他即使遇到再大的困难，再大的不幸，再大的不公平，也不会在你的面前表现出绝望、哭诉、埋怨、发牢骚，而是在你面前把一切藏在心里自己默默承受，还不停地给你制造快乐，给你带来欢乐。这个男人，能够承受巨大的痛苦，但是从不会无谓地给自己制造麻烦，因为有你。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;&quot;&gt;　　5、他为你能抵挡任何诱惑&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　这个男人不论对你还是对你们之间的感情，都是忠诚不二从不背叛的。无论他工作在什么样的圈子里，身边的朋友怎么样，对其他女人带来的性诱惑，抵抗力非常强。不是他不想，而是他能用理智控制住自己的行为，也能为自己的行为负责，哪怕你是一个从不怀疑他的人，哪怕他有一百个机会这么做。&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;&quot;&gt;　　6、他对你大度能容&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　这个男人应该非常有气度，能容一切可容之人，能容一切可容之事。他不会干涉你的私事，比如不论你是因公与客户出去应酬，还是与多年不见的同学朋友聚会，甚至是和你的初恋男友在一起。尽管他心里会很郁闷，会吃醋，但是只要你出现在他的面前，他就高兴得什么都忘了，不会在你回家后大吵大闹或者阴沉着脸半天不搭理你。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;&quot;&gt;　　7、他能调节你们的生活&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　这个男人幽默又有情趣，又懂得送你礼物，而且还有一项或者几项良好的业余爱好。你们在一起时，他总能找到你们都感兴趣的话题。不论什么时候，你们都能在一起就一个话题聊一个晚上，而且你们的话题不仅仅限于家庭琐事张家长李家短上，他可以和你谈一部韩剧，一本书。他总能想出办法装点沉闷的生活，有时间能带着你去旅游，去郊游，能带你去新开业的有特点的饭店吃晚餐，能在任何时候都能给你制造惊喜。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;&quot;&gt;　　8、他支持你的事业&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　这个男人不论多有能力，多能赚钱，他都不主张你留在家里做他和孩子的保姆，不会让你因为家庭琐事成为洗衣做饭的家庭主妇。他支持你独立、自强，有属于你自己的社交圈子，有属于你自己的同事和朋友。他不会让你出去的时候，别人只知道你是某某人的太太，而不知道你的名字。他在忙，也不会让你被家庭所累。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;&quot;&gt;　　9、他身体健康&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　这个男人身体一定很健康，有好的生活习惯，最好是没有不良嗜好，而且有锻炼身体参加各种体育活动的习惯。这个男人不一定有多么的威猛高大、魁梧伟岸，但是时刻都能精神饱满，保持男人持久地雄风.他意气风发，很阳光，很动感。不用你天天陪他去医院，也不会总代他请病假。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;&quot;&gt;　　10、他有自己的主见&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　这个男人一定要有自己的主见，不能听风就是雨人云亦云。即使他是非常孝顺的儿子，对父母的建议也是甄别的。为儿子付出很多的父母，肯定会对儿子的很多选择进行干涉，包括你们之间的事情。对于你们之间的事情，他知道能做主的只有你们两个人，不论压力有多大，他都不会活在别人的阴影里，也不会活在别人的评论中。&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;&quot;&gt;　　11、他能包容你的一切&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　这个男人如果真的爱你，会爱你的一切，包括你的坏习惯和缺点，包括你的朋友、家人的缺点和毛病，以及他们给他或你们家庭带来的烦恼和麻烦。他从不去埋怨或者指责，他会认真地对待这些事情，以你能接受的方法帮助你改掉坏习惯。他还会牺牲自己的利益去帮助你的家人和朋友，因为他知道，帮助他们，其实就是在帮助你！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　12、他具备养家糊口的能力&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　这个男人虽然不能富可敌国，但一定要有一份稳定的收入，或者有赚钱的本事，最起码养家糊口不成问题。爱情是很重要的，但是爱情脱离了生活只能是琼瑶小说里的故事，根本不可能长久。经济基础决定上层建筑，再深的感情，也禁不住困顿生活的消磨。贫贱夫妻百事哀，连柴米油盐酱醋茶都发愁的生活，还有什么心情去将就凑合呢？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;&quot;&gt;　　13、他是很自信的男人&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　这个男人应该是一个自信的人，是一个浑身散发着自信、果敢、坚毅味道的男人，能人你真正地感到放心和塌实。自信的人就能乐观，就能豁达，就能大度，无论在什么样的起点，无论经历什么样的过程，他都会用自己的努力去改变自己的命运，都会让自己追求的事业获得成功，让自己成为妻子和子女的骄傲。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　14、他和你应该很般配&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　这个男人的身高和相貌不能和你差得太远，不能看着闹心，想着恶心。就算他能满足你很高的物质生活要求，但是两人要在一起吃饭要在一起睡觉的，如果连看一眼的心情都没有，这样的生活还能维持多久？一个人的物质要求终归是有限的，而精神上的要求是无限的，谁又能和自己反感的人生活一辈子呢？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;&quot;&gt;　　15、他具备很强的沟通能力&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　这个男人在他所在的圈子里是个活跃的人物，具有一定的感召力和人格魅力，社交能力强。你带着他去参加你和同事或者同学的聚会，他能很快和你的朋友、同事找到合适的话题，在谈话中他能幽默风趣，而且说话见解独到富有哲理。&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#000000;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#000000;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;　&lt;/span&gt;　&lt;strong style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;16、他能像男人那样去战斗&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-family:宋体;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;　　这个男人不论身高如何，体重如何，但是一定要像个男人，有男子汉的气概。能一诺千金，临危不惧，宠辱不惊。考虑的是你们之间的大事，而不参与一些琐事的决策，能给你相当大的自主权和决定权。当你们与别人出现矛盾时，他总是用最简单的办法化解矛盾，还能保证你们不吃亏。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;color:#545454;font-fa